So I think there's a lot of
different directions.

00:33:05.090 --> 00:33:08.910
So I started with the college
classes because, one, that's

00:33:08.910 --> 00:33:10.710
what I have experience
with teaching.

00:33:10.710 --> 00:33:13.570
Two, the subject matter is a
little bit more well defined,

00:33:13.570 --> 00:33:16.490
so it's easier to measure.

00:33:16.490 --> 00:33:20.846
And three, there's no
complicated laws with children

00:33:20.846 --> 00:33:23.020
that are under 13 and getting
permission and all

00:33:23.020 --> 00:33:24.660
that kind of stuff.

00:33:24.660 --> 00:33:26.170
So it was easiest
to start there.

00:33:26.170 --> 00:33:28.470
But I think you you're
absolutely right, that there

00:33:28.470 --> 00:33:29.870
are other applications
