00:33:29.870 --> 00:33:32.170
And children is an important
part of it.

00:33:32.170 --> 00:33:36.770
And I think there will be
a mix there of coming at

00:33:36.770 --> 00:33:40.440
children through the schools and
coming at the schools sort

00:33:40.440 --> 00:33:43.120
of with children discovering
it on their own.

00:33:43.120 --> 00:33:45.270
And you're seeing that with
things like Khan Academy,

00:33:45.270 --> 00:33:49.120
where there are some places Khan
is the official policy of

00:33:49.120 --> 00:33:50.540
schools and they use it.

00:33:50.540 --> 00:33:54.170
But there are many more places
where kids just say my teacher

00:33:54.170 --> 00:33:56.140
said some confusing today
and I didn't get it.

00:33:56.140 --> 00:33:58.460
But I think it had the word
binomial theorem in it.

00:33:58.460 --> 00:34:01.910
And so let me see what Khan has
to say and that will be

00:34:01.910 --> 00:34:03.560
more clear.

00:34:03.560 --> 00:34:04.470
So we'll see that.

00:34:04.470 --> 00:34:06.160
And we'll also see other uses.

00:34:06.160 --> 00:34:09.040
So we'll see on-the-job
training, I think will be

00:34:09.040 --> 00:34:11.120
important-- continuing
education.

00:34:11.120 --> 00:34:14.920
And I think we'll see
non-academic subjects.

00:34:14.920 --> 00:34:17.610
How do I fix my toilet
when it breaks?

00:34:17.610 --> 00:34:20.030
We'll see better education for
things like that as well.

