00:35:58.460 --> 00:36:00.380
My question is related
to children.

00:36:00.380 --> 00:36:05.620
Beside the legal problem dealing
with small children,

00:36:05.620 --> 00:36:07.710
do you think there is a
different [INAUDIBLE]

00:36:07.710 --> 00:36:15.340
