00:36:27.780 --> 00:36:30.800
definite path for
the learning.

00:36:30.800 --> 00:36:34.160
In children, I think it's more
like knowing the world.

00:36:34.160 --> 00:36:40.340
There is experiences with
ungraded classrooms and

00:36:40.340 --> 00:36:42.380
self-guided learning.

00:36:42.380 --> 00:36:47.170
