00:42:47.370 --> 00:42:50.500
You feel much more pressure to
show up and perform when

00:42:50.500 --> 00:42:53.900
you're 1 of 10 people than
when you're 1 of 10,000.

00:42:53.900 --> 00:42:57.500
And there may be multiple sizes
of groups in between

00:42:57.500 --> 00:42:59.100
that we need to experiment
with.

00:42:59.100 --> 00:43:01.582
I think we don't know
yet what works best.

