00:43:51.180 --> 00:43:53.070
that have no access to
everything you've

00:43:53.070 --> 00:43:55.030
been talking about.

00:43:55.030 --> 00:43:55.920
PETER NORVIG: I think that's
a good question.

00:43:55.920 --> 00:44:00.990
