00:44:07.340 --> 00:44:08.670
And if we go in that direction,

00:44:08.670 --> 00:44:10.150
eventually it'll come.

00:44:10.150 --> 00:44:13.010
We're skating to where the
puck is going to be.

00:44:13.010 --> 00:44:16.520
And I think we should keep
following that, but I think

00:44:16.520 --> 00:44:19.150
you are right, that there are
places now where people don't

00:44:19.150 --> 00:44:20.230
